  "text": "Up to this point, we have argued that the FVHVaR improves the traditional VaR approach. A counterargument that could emerge is that even if the specific approach improves the old-fashioned traditional VaR, its results are comparable to the estimations of other advanced econometrical approaches? In Appendix 1, we show a comparison between FVHVaR and some advanced econometric approaches as estimated and presented in the Degiannakis et al. [CITATION_1] study.",
